    "__edge_metadata_19" [label=<
<TABLE BORDER="0" CELLBORDER="0" CELLPADDING="4">
<TR><TD ALIGN="LEFT"><B><FONT POINT-SIZE="10">Prerequisite Edge Description</FONT></B></TD></TR>
<TR><TD ALIGN="LEFT"><FONT POINT-SIZE="9" COLOR="gray35"><B>Description:</B></FONT><BR ALIGN="LEFT"/><FONT POINT-SIZE="9">Previously published systems for entailment‑tree<BR ALIGN="LEFT"/>generation against which METGEN+LMPM is compared.</FONT></TD></TR>
<TR><TD ALIGN="LEFT"><FONT POINT-SIZE="9" COLOR="gray35"><B>Explanation:</B></FONT><BR ALIGN="LEFT"/><FONT POINT-SIZE="9">Performance relative to these baselines establishes<BR ALIGN="LEFT"/>the state‑of‑the‑art claim.</FONT></TD></TR>
