<TR><TD ALIGN="LEFT"><B><FONT POINT-SIZE="10">Prerequisite Edge Description</FONT></B></TD></TR>
<TR><TD ALIGN="LEFT"><FONT POINT-SIZE="9" COLOR="gray35"><B>Description:</B></FONT><BR ALIGN="LEFT"/><FONT POINT-SIZE="9">A dataset and methodology for constructing<BR ALIGN="LEFT"/>natural‑language proof trees that explain how a set of<BR ALIGN="LEFT"/>premises entails a goal, providing the basic<BR ALIGN="LEFT"/>representation of premises, intermediate steps, and<BR ALIGN="LEFT"/>goal used throughout the paper.</FONT></TD></TR>
