<TABLE BORDER="0" CELLBORDER="0" CELLPADDING="4">
<TR><TD ALIGN="LEFT"><B><FONT POINT-SIZE="10">Prerequisite Edge Description</FONT></B></TD></TR>
<TR><TD ALIGN="LEFT"><FONT POINT-SIZE="9" COLOR="gray35"><B>Description:</B></FONT><BR ALIGN="LEFT"/><FONT POINT-SIZE="9">Prior work on constructing proof‑like entailment trees<BR ALIGN="LEFT"/>that recursively decompose hypotheses into premises<BR ALIGN="LEFT"/>and verify them against a knowledge source.</FONT></TD></TR>
<TR><TD ALIGN="LEFT"><FONT POINT-SIZE="9" COLOR="gray35"><B>Explanation:</B></FONT><BR ALIGN="LEFT"/><FONT POINT-SIZE="9">The task is motivated by and intended for use within<BR ALIGN="LEFT"/>entailment‑tree search algorithms.</FONT></TD></TR>
