    "__edge_metadata_31" [label=<
<TABLE BORDER="0" CELLBORDER="0" CELLPADDING="4">
<TR><TD ALIGN="LEFT"><B><FONT POINT-SIZE="10">Prerequisite Edge Description</FONT></B></TD></TR>
<TR><TD ALIGN="LEFT"><FONT POINT-SIZE="9" COLOR="gray35"><B>Description:</B></FONT><BR ALIGN="LEFT"/><FONT POINT-SIZE="9">Prior work on constructing entailment trees that<BR ALIGN="LEFT"/>explain answers by linking premises to conclusions via<BR ALIGN="LEFT"/>logical entailment.</FONT></TD></TR>
<TR><TD ALIGN="LEFT"><FONT POINT-SIZE="9" COLOR="gray35"><B>Explanation:</B></FONT><BR ALIGN="LEFT"/><FONT POINT-SIZE="9">Informs the design of the entailment‑graph structure<BR ALIGN="LEFT"/>used as the MDP state.</FONT></TD></TR>
