    "__edge_metadata_57" [label=<
<TABLE BORDER="0" CELLBORDER="0" CELLPADDING="4">
<TR><TD ALIGN="LEFT"><B><FONT POINT-SIZE="10">Prerequisite Edge Description</FONT></B></TD></TR>
<TR><TD ALIGN="LEFT"><FONT POINT-SIZE="9" COLOR="gray35"><B>Description:</B></FONT><BR ALIGN="LEFT"/><FONT POINT-SIZE="9">A dataset of multi‑step entailment trees (average 6.6<BR ALIGN="LEFT"/>nodes) paired with QA instances, used to train and<BR ALIGN="LEFT"/>evaluate natural‑language proof generation systems.</FONT></TD></TR>
<TR><TD ALIGN="LEFT"><FONT POINT-SIZE="9" COLOR="gray35"><B>Explanation:</B></FONT><BR ALIGN="LEFT"/><FONT POINT-SIZE="9">ConDec is trained and evaluated on EntailmentBank; the<BR ALIGN="LEFT"/>dataset defines the task format (hypothesis,<BR ALIGN="LEFT"/>supporting facts, stepwise proof) that the method<BR ALIGN="LEFT"/>addresses.</FONT></TD></TR>
