<TR><TD ALIGN="LEFT"><FONT POINT-SIZE="9" COLOR="gray35"><B>Description:</B></FONT><BR ALIGN="LEFT"/><FONT POINT-SIZE="9">Generating explicit, tree‑structured explanations<BR ALIGN="LEFT"/>(entailment or proof trees) for natural‑language<BR ALIGN="LEFT"/>reasoning tasks to improve interpretability and enable<BR ALIGN="LEFT"/>verification of intermediate steps.</FONT></TD></TR>
