<TR><TD ALIGN="LEFT"><B><FONT POINT-SIZE="10">Prerequisite Edge Description</FONT></B></TD></TR>
<TR><TD ALIGN="LEFT"><FONT POINT-SIZE="9" COLOR="gray35"><B>Description:</B></FONT><BR ALIGN="LEFT"/><FONT POINT-SIZE="9">Prior work on multi‑step reasoning tasks and<BR ALIGN="LEFT"/>compositional benchmarks that define reasoning hops,<BR ALIGN="LEFT"/>distractors, and reduction of relational chains.</FONT></TD></TR>
<TR><TD ALIGN="LEFT"><FONT POINT-SIZE="9" COLOR="gray35"><B>Explanation:</B></FONT><BR ALIGN="LEFT"/><FONT POINT-SIZE="9">ACCORD’s reasoning trees, hops, and distractor<BR ALIGN="LEFT"/>concepts are built upon established notions of<BR ALIGN="LEFT"/>multi‑hop reasoning and compositional scaling.</FONT></TD></TR>
<TR><TD ALIGN="LEFT"><FONT POINT-SIZE="10">strength: strong; depth: 0</FONT></TD></TR>
